# Arca Docs

Mintlify documentation site. Pages are MDX with YAML frontmatter; navigation in `docs.json`.

- Run `mint dev` to preview locally
- Run `mint broken-links` to check links
- Update docs whenever the v1 API changes (new endpoints, modified responses, fields)

Use "workspace" not "project"; use active voice and second person.
